txt.en: Aganbâr the Cruel, Overseer of Mornaur, keeps his workers hard at task despite the fact that the war is lost.
Aganbâr the Cruel, Overseer of Mornaur, keeps his workers hard at task despite the fact that the war is lost. What plans or orders he follows, no good can come of these machinations.
You have defeated Aganbâr the Cruel, Overseer of Mornaur, who kept his workers hard at task, no matter Sauron's fall.
Defeat Overseer Aganbâr the Cruel in Mornaur, on the south slope of Udûn.
